			<div id="left-column">
				<div id="about-area">
					<p><b>Anxiety</b> is a super-lightweight To-do list application for Mac OS X Leopard that synchronizes with iCal and Mail. Its aim is to provide a streamlined, easily accessible interface to add and check off your tasks, while remaining poised to melt into the background at a moments notice.</p>
				</div>
